spec_data.Name: perl-Test-Strict
spec_data.Description:
"Test::Strict" lets you check the syntax, presence of "use strict;" and
"use warnings;" in your perl code.  It reports its results in standard
"Test::Simple" fashion.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 04:59:19 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Check syntax, presence of use strict/warnings, and test coverage
